{"tid":1844831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發： 高比拜仁意外身亡","createTime":"2020-01-26T20:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T21:18:53.000Z","uid":46996,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"850be3f1eb9c8640fb6d148a3dcb6114773ae74e","tid":1844831,"uid":46996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T20:18:37.000Z","msg":"人生無常<br />\n<br />\n美國傳媒周日報道，NBA洛杉磯湖人退休球星高比拜恩（Kobe Bryant）周日在加州洛杉磯市郊墜機身亡，終年41歲。<br />\n<br />\nTMZ網站報道，高比與另外四人乘搭他的私人直升機，在卡拉巴薩斯（Calabasas）墜毀。墜機原因調查中。<br />\n<br />\n高比生於美國費城，1996年首次在NBA出賽，2016年球季結束後退休，在他為洛杉磯湖人效力的20年職業生涯中，總得分達到33,643分，位居NBA歷史第三位，直至周六才被勒邦占士（LeBron James）超越。<br />\n<br />\n高比遺下妻子和四女兒。<br />\n<br />\n點解死的唔係777<br />\nR.i.p"},{"pid":"af5b35a7e80bb0ae59224e9d7c074ab792859ee4","tid":1844831,"uid":172349,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T20:19:34.000Z","msg":"死LeBron James都好呀，點解要死Kobe"},{"pid":"418740bcd8742ff28f1566d8f64c774865ec67bd","tid":1844831,"uid":211317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T20:20:33.000Z","msg":"RIP."},{"pid":"160ecef554f121e61ab5770830479588bb6058fa","tid":1844831,"uid":46996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T20:23:29.000Z","msg":"一代巨星就突然走左<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d295f38cddb61afbf848fcca9a1351d5409eeb20","tid":1844831,"uid":211317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T20:24:46.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"e5f59cc26869800a10b0e735d7b82f36f32724a2","tid":1844831,"uid":46996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T21:18:53.000Z","msg":"仲有個二女都死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}